      elements
    </li>
  </ul>
  <ul>
    <h2>Artistically Driven</h2>
    <li>
      Prioritizes mood, composition, and visual storytelling over corporate
      polish
    </li>
    <li>
      Often includes hand-drawn elements, textures, painterly color palettes, or
      collage-style layouts
    </li>
    <li>
